body: Am I the only one tired of the female love interest who's so amazing and awesome that "even some girls confess to her" trope?It just feels even more hamfisted that the writer wants so badly for you to see how wonderful she is to the point they're practically mary sues. I dunno, I just feel like it'd be a nice change in pace if a dude was so amazing that other guys confess to him even tho I'm not even remotely gay or bi. But when this line gets so over saturated and overused in practically every doujin/animemanga I just roll my eyes and look somewhere else that doesn't have that. Maybe it's just me or I'm expecting too much
